The uploader hasn't made any mistake - it's just Adobe's confusing version numbering system. CS = Creative Suite, which contains InDesign 3.0, Photoshop 8, etc. The latest Creative Suite is CS3, which contains InDesign 5.0 and Photoshop 10, etc.
